{"tid":1386079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講堅, 你班和理非夠唔夠膽唔交稅?","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:11:57.000Z","uid":12558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0606e28debcce31980e3a6b23f8a8b8d312f82ad","tid":1386079,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:51:44.000Z","msg":"衝又唔夠膽衝<br />\n罷工又話要返工<br />\n塞地鐵又阻住你返工<br />\n<br />\n你夠唔夠膽唔交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n稅務局指出，一旦納稅人未能準時交稅，當局局長可據《稅務條例》提出檢控或罰款等，目前的安排是對逾期交稅的人士即時加徵5%附加費，假如打工仔的欠款逾期多於6個月，則是基於欠款及5%附加費之上，再加徵10%的附加費。而且，稅務局可以採取「非常手段」收回稅款，包括向打工仔的僱主或租客等扣稅，變相把打工仔欠稅的事情「唱通街」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，錢銀和面子問題可能已屬事小，因為稅務局還可以對欠稅人士執行一系列的法律行動。最直接的一步，是稅務局向區域法院申請發出傳訊令狀，對欠稅人士進行民事起訴，追討欠稅，欠稅人士屆時或面臨更大的損失，因為可能要繳付法院費用、定額訟費及由申索訴訟開始至判定債項全數清繳日期間的利息。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">假如納稅人仍未能清繳債項，稅務局還有兩招「殺手鐧」可用，第一招是向法院申請扣押欠稅人士的財產，甚至提出破產或清盤申請，同時可以配搭第二招，向法院申請阻止離境指示，阻止有關人士離開香港。</span><br />\n<br />\n據稅務局的網站，其實打工仔一時間手頭緊，是可以寫信給當局申請分期繳付稅項，以免因欠稅衍生更大的財務問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dab46b67393e94d281a27510d310ecbb48da02","tid":1386079,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:52:03.000Z","msg":"要大部人肯唔交先有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的, 熱心市民的支持(現金券)已到位, 請有需要的年輕手足黎搵我地拎, 如果真係唔方便出面/想慳車錢的可以考慮搵人代領<br />\n(請TG搵我地講低代領人的名/代號之類/你叫代領人黎到講你的TG ID以茲識別)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fightforh_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffightforh_k&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuc5qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=9182f22e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fightforh_k</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月30)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuc5qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=f59c1064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000%2F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuc5qU0izJB5q5dcgVJazxes%3D&h=6c38e97c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/</a>"},{"pid":"900854d3d459492f513b14f88d0e607a845e47d2","tid":1386079,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"之前先講過，唔交稅冇用，佢可以直接喺你戶口扣，但你交多咗，佢退返比你，稅局要做好多手續，煩撚死佢仲好"},{"pid":"a9032cc76d1da45ca1433bc815d16173ac5fc23f","tid":1386079,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900854d3d459492f513b14f88d0e607a845e47d2","tid":1386079,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"之前